<~>*NL*<~>variation<~>which<~>takes<~>place<~>according<~>to<~>the<~>law<~>of<~>causality<~>,<~>implies<~>*NL*<~>always<~>a<~>determined<~>part<~>of<~>space<~>and<~>a<~>determined<~>part<~>of<~>time<~>together<~>*NL*<~>and<~>in<~>union<~>.<~>Thus<~>causality<~>unites<~>space<~>with<~>time<~>.<~>But<~>we<~>found<~>that<~>the<~>*NL*<~>whole<~>essence<~>of<~>matter<~>consisted<~>in<~>action<~>,<~>i.e.<~>,<~>in<~>causation<~>,<~>*NL*<~>consequently<~>space<~>and<~>time<~>must<~>also<~>be<~>united<~>in<~>matter<~>,<~>that<~>is<~>to<~>say<~>,<~>*NL*<~>matter<~>must<~>take<~>to<~>itself<~>at<~>once<~>the<~>distinguishing<~>qualities<~>both<~>of<~>*NL*<~>space<~>and<~>time<~>,<~>however<~>much<~>these<~>may<~>be<~>opposed<~>to<~>each<~>other<~>,<~>and<~>must<~>*NL*<~>unite<~>in<~>itself<~>what<~>is<~>impossible<~>for<~>each<~>of<~>these<~>independently<~>,<~>that<~>*NL*<~>is<~>,<~>the<~>fleeting<~>course<~>of<~>time<~>,<~>with<~>the<~>rigid<~>unchangeable<~>perduration<~>*NL*<~>of<~>space<~>:<~>infinite<~>divisibility<~>it<~>receives<~>from<~>both<~>.<~>It<~>is<~>for<~>this<~>*NL*<~>reason<~>that<~>we<~>find<~>that<~>co-existence<~>,<~>which<~>could<~>neither<~>be<~>in<~>time<~>*NL*<~>alone<~>,<~>for<~>time<~>has<~>no<~>contiguity<~>,<~>nor<~>in<~>space<~>alone<~>,<~>for<~>space<~>has<~>no<~>*NL*<~>before<~>,<~>after<~>,<~>or<~>now<~>,<~>is<~>first<~>established<~>through<~>matter<~>.<~>But<~>the<~>*NL*<~>co-existence<~>of<~>many<~>things<~>constitutes<~>,<~>in<~>fact<~>,<~>the<~>essence<~>of<~>reality<~>,<~>*NL*<~>for<~>through<~>it<~>permanence<~>first<~>becomes<~>possible<~>;<~>for<~>permanence<~>is<~>only<~>*NL*<~>knowable<~>in<~>the<~>change<~>of<~>something<~>which<~>is<~>present<~>along<~>with<~>what<~>is<~>*NL*<~>permanent<~>,<~>while<~>on<~>the<~>other<~>hand<~>it<~>is<~>only<~>because<~>something<~>permanent<~>*NL*<~>is<~>present<~>along<~>with<~>what<~>changes<~>,<~>that<~>the<~>latter<~>gains<~>the<~>special<~>*NL*<~>character<~>of<~>change<~>,<~>i.e.<~>,<~>the<