L*<~>arises<~>.<~>This<~>relation<~>is<~>no<~>conclusion<~>in<~>abstract<~>conceptions<~>;<~>it<~>does<~>*NL*<~>not<~>arise<~>from<~>reflection<~>,<~>nor<~>is<~>it<~>arbitrary<~>,<~>but<~>immediate<~>,<~>necessary<~>,<~>*NL*<~>and<~>certain<~>.<~>It<~>is<~>the<~>method<~>of<~>knowing<~>of<~>the<~>pure<~>understanding<~>,<~>*NL*<~>without<~>which<~>there<~>could<~>be<~>no<~>perception<~>;<~>there<~>would<~>only<~>remain<~>a<~>dull<~>*NL*<~>plant-like<~>consciousness<~>of<~>the<~>changes<~>of<~>the<~>immediate<~>object<~>,<~>which<~>*NL*<~>would<~>succeed<~>each<~>other<~>in<~>an<~>utterly<~>unmeaning<~>way<~>,<~>except<~>in<~>so<~>far<~>as<~>*NL*<~>they<~>might<~>have<~>a<~>meaning<~>for<~>the<~>will<~>either<~>as<~>pain<~>or<~>pleasure<~>.<~>But<~>as<~>*NL*<~>with<~>the<~>rising<~>of<~>the<~>sun<~>the<~>visible<~>world<~>appears<~>,<~>so<~>at<~>one<~>stroke<~>,<~>*NL*<~>the<~>understanding<~>,<~>by<~>means<~>of<~>its<~>one<~>simple<~>function<~>,<~>changes<~>the<~>dull<~>,<~>*NL*<~>meaningless<~>sensation<~>into<~>perception<~>.<~>What<~>the<~>eye<~>,<~>the<~>ear<~>,<~>or<~>the<~>hand<~>*NL*<~>feels<~>,<~>is<~>not<~>perception<~>;<~>it<~>is<~>merely<~>its<~>data<~>.<~>By<~>the<~>understanding<~>*NL*<~>passing<~>from<~>the<~>effect<~>to<~>the<~>cause<~>,<~>the<~>world<~>first<~>appears<~>as<~>*NL*<~>perception<~>extended<~>in<~>space<~>,<~>varying<~>in<~>respect<~>of<~>form<~>,<~>persistent<~>*NL*<~>through<~>all<~>time<~>in<~>respect<~>of<~>matter<~>;<~>for<~>the<~>understanding<~>unites<~>space<~>*NL*<~>and<~>time<~>in<~>the<~>idea<~>of<~>matter<~>,<~>that<~>is<~>,<~>causal<~>action<~>.<~>As<~>the<~>world<~>as<~>*NL*<~>idea<~>exists<~>only<~>through<~>the<~>understanding<~>,<~>so<~>also<~>it<~>exists<~>only<~>for<~>the<~>*NL*<~>understanding<~>.<~>In<~>the<~>first<~>chapter<~>of<~>my<~>essay<~>on<~>``<~>Light<~>and<~>Colour<~>,<~>''<~>I<~>*NL*<~>have<~>already<~>explained<~>how<~>the<~>understanding<~>constructs<~>perceptions<~>out<~>of<~>*NL*<~>the<~>data<~>suppli