*NL*<~>as<~>the<~>ultimate<~>ground<~>of<~>explanation<~>something<~>objective<~>,<~>whether<~>it<~>be<~>*NL*<~>matter<~>in<~>the<~>abstract<~>,<~>simply<~>as<~>it<~>is<~>thought<~>,<~>or<~>after<~>it<~>has<~>taken<~>*NL*<~>form<~>,<~>is<~>empirically<~>given<~>--<~>that<~>is<~>to<~>say<~>,<~>is<~>substance<~>,<~>the<~>chemical<~>*NL*<~>element<~>with<~>its<~>primary<~>relations<~>.<~>Some<~>such<~>thing<~>it<~>takes<~>,<~>as<~>existing<~>*NL*<~>absolutely<~>and<~>in<~>itself<~>,<~>in<~>order<~>that<~>it<~>may<~>evolve<~>organic<~>nature<~>and<~>*NL*<~>finally<~>the<~>knowing<~>subject<~>from<~>it<~>,<~>and<~>explain<~>them<~>adequately<~>by<~>means<~>*NL*<~>of<~>it<~>;<~>whereas<~>in<~>truth<~>all<~>that<~>is<~>objective<~>is<~>already<~>determined<~>as<~>*NL*<~>such<~>in<~>manifold<~>ways<~>by<~>the<~>knowing<~>subject<~>through<~>its<~>forms<~>of<~>knowing<~>,<~>*NL*<~>and<~>presupposes<~>them<~>;<~>and<~>consequently<~>it<~>entirely<~>disappears<~>if<~>we<~>think<~>*NL*<~>the<~>subject<~>away<~>.<~>Thus<~>materialism<~>is<~>the<~>attempt<~>to<~>explain<~>what<~>is<~>*NL*<~>immediately<~>given<~>us<~>by<~>what<~>is<~>given<~>us<~>indirectly<~>.<~>All<~>that<~>is<~>*NL*<~>objective<~>,<~>extended<~>,<~>active<~>--<~>that<~>is<~>to<~>say<~>,<~>all<~>that<~>is<~>material<~>--<~>is<~>*NL*<~>regarded<~>by<~>materialism<~>as<~>affording<~>so<~>solid<~>a<~>basis<~>for<~>its<~>explanation<~>,<~>*NL*<~>that<~>a<~>reduction<~>of<~>everything<~>to<~>this<~>can<~>leave<~>nothing<~>to<~>be<~>desired<~>*NL*<~>-LRB-<~>especially<~>if<~>in<~>ultimate<~>analysis<~>this<~>reduction<~>should<~>resolve<~>itself<~>*NL*<~>into<~>action<~>and<~>reaction<~>-RRB-<~>.<~>But<~>we<~>have<~>shown<~>that<~>all<~>this<~>is<~>given<~>*NL*<~>indirectly<~>and<~>in<~>the<~>highest<~>degree<~>determined<~>,<~>and<~>is<~>therefore<~>merely<~>a<~>*NL*<~>relatively<~>present<~>object<~>,<~>for<~>it<~>has<~>passed<~>through<~>the<~>machinery<~>and<~>*NL*<~>manufactory<~>of<~>the<~>brain<~>,<~>and<~>has<~>thus<~>come<~>under<~>the<~>forms<~>of<~>space<~>,<~>time<~>*NL*<~>and<~>causality<~>,<~>by<~>means<~>of<~>which<~>it<~>is<~>first<~>presented<~>to<~>us<~>as<~>extended<~>*NL*<~>in<~>space<~>and<~>ever<~>active<~>in<~>time<~>.<~>From<~>such<~>an<~>indirectly<~>given<~>object<~>,<~>*NL*<~>materialism<~>seeks<~>to<~>explain<~>what<~>is<~>immediately<~>given<~>,<~>the<~>idea<~>-LRB-<~>in<~>which<~>*NL*<~>alone<~>the<~>object<~>that<~>materialism<~>starts<~>with<~>exists<~>-RRB-<~>,<~>and<~>finally<~>even<~>*NL*<~>the<~>will<~>from<~>which<~>all<~>those<~>fundamental<~>forces<~>,<~>that<~>manifest<~>*NL*<~>themselves<~>,<~>under<~>the<~>guidance<~>of<~>causes<~>,<~>and<~>therefore<~>according<~>to<~>law<~>,<~>*NL*<~>are<~>in<~>truth<~>to<~>be<~>explained<~>.<~>To<~>the<~>assertion<~>that<~>thought<~>is<~>a<~>*NL*<~>modification<~>of<~>matter<~>we<~>may<~>always<~>,<~>with<~>equal<~>right<~>,<~>oppose<~>the<~>*NL*<~>contrary<~>assertion<~>that<~>all<~>matter<~>is<~>merely<~>the<~>modification<~>of<~>the<~>*NL*<~>knowing<~>subject<~>,<~>as<~>its<~>idea<~>.<~>Yet<~>the<~>aim<~>and<~>ideal<~>of<~>all<~>natural<~>science<~>*NL*<~>is<~>at<~>bottom<~>a<~>consistent<~>materialism<~>.<~>The<~>recognition<~>here<~>of<~>the<~>obvious<~>*NL*<~>impossibility<~>of<~>such<~>a<~>system<~>establishes<~>another<~>truth<~>which<~>will<~>appear<~>*NL*<~>in<~>the<~>course<~>of<~>our<~>exposition<~>,<~>the<~>truth<~>that<~>all<~>science<~>properly<~>so<~>*NL*<~>called<~>,<~>by<~>which<~>I<~>understand<~>systematic<~>knowledge<~>under<~>the<~>guidance<~>of<~>*NL*<~>the<~>principle<~>of<~>sufficient<~>reason<~>,<~>can<~>never<~>reach<~>its<~>final<~>goal<~>,<~>nor<~>*NL*<~>give<~>a<~>complete<~>and<~>adequate<~>explanation<~>:<~>for<~>it<~>is<~>not<~>concerned<~>with<~>the<~>*NL*<~>inmost<~>nature<~>of<~>the<~>world<~>,<~>it<~>can<~>not<~>get<~>beyond<~>the<~>idea<~>;<~>indeed<~>,<~>it<~>*NL*<~>really<~>teaches<~>nothing<~>more<~>than<~>the<~>relation<~>of<~>one<~>idea<~>to<~>another<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>Every<~>science<~>must<~>start<~>from<~>two<~>principal<~>data<~>.<~>One<~>of<~>these<~>is<~>always<~>*NL*<~>the<~>principle<~>of<~>sufficient<~>reason<~>in<~>some<~>form<~>or<~>another<~>,<~>as<~>organon<~>;<~>*NL*<~>the<~>other<~>is<~>its<~>special<~>object<~>as<~>problem<~>.<~>Thus<~>,<~>for<~>example<~>,<~>geometry<~>*NL*<~>has<~>space<~>as<~>problem<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>ground<~>of<~>existence<~>in<~>space<~>as<~>organon<~>.<~>*NL*<~>Arithmetic<~>has<~>time<~>as<~>problem<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>ground<~>of<~>existence<~>in<~>time<~>as<~>*NL*<~>organon<~>.<~>Logic<~>has<~>the<~>combination<~>of<~>concepts<~>as<~>such<~>as<~>problem<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>*NL*<~>ground<~>of<~>knowledge<~>as<~>organon<~>.<~>History<~>has<~>the<~>past<~>acts<~>of<~>men<~>treated<~>*NL*<~>as<~>a<~>whole<~>as<~>problem<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>law<~>of<~>human<~>motives<~>as<~>organon<~>.<~>Natural<~>*NL*<~>science<~>has<~>matter<~>as<~>problem<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>law<~>of<~>causality<~>as<~>organon<~>.<~>Its<~>*NL*<~>end<~>and<~>aim<~>is<~>therefore<~>,<~>by<~>the<~>guidance<~>of<~>causality<~>,<~>to<~>refer<~>all<~>*NL*<~>possible<~>states<~>of<~>matter<~>to<~>other<~>states<~>,<~>and<~>ultimately<~>to<~>one<~>single<~>*NL*<~>state<~>;<~>and<~>again<~>to<~>deduce<~>these<~>states<~>from<~>each<~>other<~>,<~>and<~>ultimately<~>*NL*<~>from<~>one<~>single<~>state<~>.<~>Thus<~>two<~>states<~>of<~>matter<~>stand<~>over<~>against<~>each<~>*NL*<~>other<~>in<~>natural<~>science<~>as<~>extremes<~>:<~>that<~>state<~>in<~>which<~>matter<~>is<~>*NL*<~>furthest<~>from<~>being<~>the<~>immediate<~>object<~>of<~>the<~>subject<~>,<~>and<~>that<~>state<~>in<~>*NL*<~>which<~>it<~>is<~>most<~>completely<~>such<~>an<~>immediate<~>object<~>,<~>i.e.<~>,<~>the<~>most<~>*NL*<~>dead<~>and<~>crude<~>matter<~>,<~>the<~>primary<~>element<~>,<~>as<~>the<~>one<~>extreme<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>*NL*<~>human<~>organism<~>as<~>the<~>other<~>.<~>Natural<~>science<~>as<~>chemistry<~>seeks<~>for<~>the<~>*NL*<~>first<~>,<~>as<~>phys