<~>path<~>from<~>the<~>general<~>to<~>the<~>particular<~>,<~>distinguishes<~>it<~>from<~>*NL*<~>ordinary<~>rational<~>knowledge<~>;<~>therefore<~>,<~>systematic<~>form<~>is<~>an<~>essential<~>*NL*<~>and<~>characteristic<~>feature<~>of<~>science<~>.<~>The<~>combination<~>of<~>the<~>most<~>general<~>*NL*<~>concept-spheres<~>of<~>every<~>science<~>,<~>that<~>is<~>,<~>the<~>knowledge<~>of<~>its<~>first<~>*NL*<~>principles<~>,<~>is<~>the<~>indispensable<~>condition<~>of<~>mastering<~>it<~>;<~>how<~>far<~>we<~>*NL*<~>advance<~>from<~>these<~>to<~>the<~>more<~>special<~>propositions<~>is<~>a<~>matter<~>of<~>choice<~>,<~>*NL*<~>and<~>does<~>not<~>increase<~>the<~>thoroughness<~>but<~>only<~>the<~>extent<~>of<~>our<~>*NL*<~>knowledge<~>of<~>the<~>science<~>.<~>The<~>number<~>of<~>the<~>first<~>principles<~>to<~>which<~>all<~>*NL*<~>the<~>rest<~>are<~>subordinated<~>,<~>varies<~>greatly<~>in<~>the<~>different<~>sciences<~>,<~>so<~>*NL*<~>that<~>in<~>some<~>there<~>is<~>more<~>subordination<~>,<~>in<~>others<~>more<~>co-ordination<~>;<~>*NL*<~>and<~>in<~>this<~>respect<~>,<~>the<~>former<~>make<~>greater<~>claims<~>upon<~>the<~>judgment<~>,<~>the<~>*NL*<~>latter<~>upon<~>the<~>memory<~>.<~>It<~>was<~>known<~>to<~>the<~>schoolmen<~>,<~>-LRB-<~>19<~>-RRB-<~>that<~>,<~>as<~>the<~>*NL*<~>syllogism<~>requires<~>two<~>premises<~>,<~>no<~>science<~>can<~>proceed<~>from<~>a<~>single<~>*NL*<~>first<~>principle<~>which<~>can<~>not<~>be<~>the<~>subject<~>of<~>further<~>deduction<~>,<~>but<~>must<~>*NL*<~>have<~>several<~>,<~>at<~>least<~>two<~>.<~>The<~>specially<~>classifying<~>sciences<~>:<~>Zoology<~>,<~>*NL*<~>Botany<~>,<~>and<~>also<~>Physics<~>and<~>Chemistry<~>,<~>inasmuch<~>as<~>they<~>refer<~>all<~>*NL*<~>inorganic<~>action<~>to<~>a<~>few<~>fundamental<~>forces<~>,<~>have<~>most<~>subordination<~>;<~>*NL*<~>history<~>,<~>on<~>the<~>other<~>hand<~>,<~>has<~>really<~>none<~>at<~>all<~>;<~>for<~>the<~>general<~>in<~>it<~>*NL*<~>consists<~>merely<~>in<~>the<~>survey<~>of<~>the<~>pri