>identical<~>in<~>spite<~>of<~>a<~>*NL*<~>partial<~>difference<~>,<~>all<~>in<~>accordance<~>with<~>the<~>end<~>and<~>intention<~>which<~>in<~>*NL*<~>each<~>case<~>is<~>in<~>view<~>;<~>all<~>this<~>is<~>done<~>by<~>the<~>faculty<~>of<~>judgment<~>.<~>*NL*<~>Deficiency<~>in<~>judgment<~>is<~>silliness<~>.<~>The<~>silly<~>man<~>fails<~>to<~>grasp<~>,<~>now<~>*NL*<~>the<~>partial<~>or<~>relative<~>difference<~>of<~>concepts<~>which<~>in<~>one<~>aspect<~>are<~>*NL*<~>identical<~>,<~>now<~>the<~>identity<~>of<~>concepts<~>which<~>are<~>relatively<~>or<~>partially<~>*NL*<~>different<~>.<~>To<~>this<~>explanation<~>of<~>the<~>faculty<~>of<~>judgment<~>,<~>moreover<~>,<~>*NL*<~>Kant<~>'s<~>division<~>of<~>it<~>into<~>reflecting<~>and<~>subsuming<~>judgment<~>may<~>be<~>*NL*<~>applied<~>,<~>according<~>as<~>it<~>passes<~>from<~>the<~>perceived<~>objects<~>to<~>the<~>*NL*<~>concepts<~>,<~>or<~>from<~>the<~>latter<~>to<~>the<~>former<~>;<~>in<~>both<~>cases<~>always<~>mediating<~>*NL*<~>between<~>empirical<~>knowledge<~>of<~>the<~>understanding<~>and<~>the<~>reflective<~>*NL*<~>knowledge<~>of<~>the<~>reason<~>.<~>There<~>can<~>be<~>no<~>truth<~>which<~>could<~>be<~>brought<~>out<~>*NL*<~>by<~>means<~>of<~>syllogisms<~>alone<~>;<~>and<~>the<~>necessity<~>of<~>establishing<~>truth<~>by<~>*NL*<~>means<~>of<~>syllogisms<~>is<~>merely<~>relative<~>,<~>indeed<~>subjective<~>.<~>Since<~>all<~>*NL*<~>demonstration<~>is<~>syllogistic<~>,<~>in<~>the<~>case<~>of<~>a<~>new<~>truth<~>we<~>must<~>first<~>*NL*<~>seek<~>,<~>not<~>for<~>a<~>demonstration<~>,<~>but<~>for<~>direct<~>evidence<~>,<~>and<~>only<~>in<~>the<~>*NL*<~>absence<~>of<~>such<~>evidence<~>is<~>a<~>demonstration<~>to<~>be<~>temporarily<~>made<~>use<~>of<~>.<~>*NL*<~>No<~>science<~>is<~>susceptible<~>of<~>demonstration<~>throughout<~>any<~>more<~>than<~>a<~>*NL*<~>building<~>can<~>stand<~>in<~>the<~>air<~>;<~>all<~>its<~>demonstrations<~>must<~>ultimately<~>rest<~>*NL*<~>upon<~>what<~>is<~>perceived<~>,<~>and<~>consequently<~