cessity<~>.<~>For<~>example<~>,<~>that<~>matter<~>is<~>permanent<~>,<~>*NL*<~>that<~>is<~>,<~>can<~>neither<~>come<~>into<~>being<~>nor<~>pass<~>away<~>,<~>we<~>know<~>directly<~>as<~>*NL*<~>negative<~>truth<~>;<~>for<~>our<~>pure<~>intuition<~>or<~>perception<~>of<~>space<~>and<~>time<~>*NL*<~>gives<~>the<~>possibility<~>of<~>motion<~>;<~>in<~>the<~>law<~>of<~>causality<~>the<~>understanding<~>*NL*<~>affords<~>us<~>the<~>possibility<~>of<~>change<~>of<~>form<~>and<~>quality<~>,<~>but<~>we<~>lack<~>*NL*<~>powers<~>of<~>the<~>imagination<~>for<~>conceiving<~>the<~>coming<~>into<~>being<~>or<~>passing<~>*NL*<~>away<~>of<~>matter<~>.<~>Therefore<~>that<~>truth<~>has<~>at<~>all<~>times<~>been<~>evident<~>to<~>all<~>*NL*<~>men<~>everywhere<~>,<~>nor<~>has<~>it<~>ever<~>been<~>seriously<~>doubted<~>;<~>and<~>this<~>could<~>not<~>*NL*<~>be<~>the<~>case<~>if<~>it<~>had<~>no<~>other<~>ground<~>of<~>knowledge<~>than<~>the<~>abstruse<~>and<~>*NL*<~>exceedingly<~>subtle<~>proof<~>of<~>Kant<~>.<~>But<~>besides<~>this<~>,<~>I<~>have<~>found<~>Kant<~>'s<~>*NL*<~>proof<~>to<~>be<~>false<~>-LRB-<~>as<~>is<~>explained<~>in<~>the<~>Appendix<~>-RRB-<~>,<~>and<~>have<~>shown<~>above<~>*NL*<~>that<~>the<~>permanence<~>of<~>matter<~>is<~>to<~>be<~>deduced<~>,<~>not<~>from<~>the<~>share<~>which<~>*NL*<~>time<~>has<~>in<~>the<~>possibility<~>of<~>experience<~>,<~>but<~>from<~>the<~>share<~>which<~>*NL*<~>belongs<~>to<~>space<~>.<~>The<~>true<~>foundation<~>of<~>all<~>truths<~>which<~>in<~>this<~>sense<~>*NL*<~>are<~>called<~>metaphysical<~>,<~>that<~>is<~>,<~>abstract<~>expressions<~>of<~>the<~>necessary<~>*NL*<~>and<~>universal<~>forms<~>of<~>knowledge<~>,<~>can<~>not<~>itself<~>lie<~>in<~>abstract<~>*NL*<~>principles<~>;<~>but<~>only<~>in<~>the<~>immediate<~>consciousness<~>of<~>the<~>forms<~>of<~>the<~>*NL*<~>idea<~>communicating<~>itself<~>in<~>apodictic<~>assertions<~>a<~>priori<~>,<~>and<~>fearing<~>*NL*<~>no<~>refutation<~>.<~>But<~>if<~>we<~>yet<~>desire<~>to<~>give<~>a<~>proof<~>of