<~>means<~>to<~>greater<~>certainty<~>.<~>It<~>is<~>easier<~>to<~>*NL*<~>discover<~>the<~>nature<~>of<~>an<~>animal<~>,<~>by<~>means<~>of<~>the<~>species<~>to<~>which<~>it<~>*NL*<~>belongs<~>,<~>and<~>so<~>on<~>through<~>the<~>genus<~>,<~>family<~>,<~>order<~>,<~>and<~>class<~>,<~>than<~>to<~>*NL*<~>examine<~>on<~>every<~>occasion<~>the<~>animal<~>presented<~>to<~>us<~>:<~>but<~>the<~>truth<~>of<~>all<~>*NL*<~>propositions<~>arrived<~>at<~>syllogistically<~>is<~>always<~>conditioned<~>by<~>and<~>*NL*<~>ultimately<~>dependent<~>upon<~>some<~>truth<~>which<~>rests<~>not<~>upon<~>reasoning<~>but<~>*NL*<~>upon<~>perception<~>.<~>If<~>this<~>perception<~>were<~>always<~>as<~>much<~>within<~>our<~>reach<~>*NL*<~>as<~>a<~>deduction<~>through<~>syllogisms<~>,<~>then<~>it<~>would<~>be<~>in<~>every<~>respect<~>*NL*<~>preferable<~>.<~>For<~>every<~>deduction<~>from<~>concepts<~>is<~>exposed<~>to<~>great<~>danger<~>*NL*<~>of<~>error<~>,<~>on<~>account<~>of<~>the<~>fact<~>we<~>have<~>considered<~>above<~>,<~>that<~>so<~>many<~>*NL*<~>spheres<~>lie<~>partly<~>within<~>each<~>other<~>,<~>and<~>that<~>their<~>content<~>is<~>often<~>*NL*<~>vague<~>or<~>uncertain<~>.<~>This<~>is<~>illustrated<~>by<~>a<~>multitude<~>of<~>demonstrations<~>*NL*<~>of<~>false<~>doctrines<~>and<~>sophisms<~>of<~>every<~>kind<~>.<~>Syllogisms<~>are<~>indeed<~>*NL*<~>perfectly<~>certain<~>as<~>regards<~>form<~>,<~>but<~>they<~>are<~>very<~>uncertain<~>on<~>account<~>*NL*<~>of<~>their<~>matter<~>,<~>the<~>concepts<~>.<~>For<~>,<~>on<~>the<~>one<~>hand<~>,<~>the<~>spheres<~>of<~>these<~>*NL*<~>are<~>not<~>sufficiently<~>sharply<~>defined<~>,<~>and<~>,<~>on<~>the<~>other<~>hand<~>,<~>they<~>*NL*<~>intersect<~>each<~>other<~>in<~>so<~>many<~>ways<~>that<~>one<~>sphere<~>is<~>in<~>part<~>contained<~>*NL*<~>in<~>many<~>others<~>,<~>and<~>we<~>may<~>pass<~>at<~>will<~>from<~>it<~>to<~>one<~>or<~>another<~>of<~>*NL*<~>these<~>,<~>and<~>from<~>this<~>sphere<~>again<~>to<~>others<~>,<~>as<~>we<~>have<~>already<~>shown<~>.<~>Or<~>,<~>*NL*<~>in<~>other<~>words<~>,<~>the<~>minor<~>term<~>and<~>also<~>the<~>middle<~>can<~>always<~>be<~>*NL*<~>subordinated<~>to<~>different<~>concepts<~>,<~>from<~>which<~>we<~>may<~>choose<~>at<~>will<~>the<~>*NL*<~>major<~>and<~>the<~>middle<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>nature<~>of<~>the<~>conclusion<~>depends<~>on<~>this<~>*NL*<~>choice<~>.<~>Consequently<~>immediate<~>evidence<~>is<~>always<~>much<~>to<~>be<~>preferred<~>to<~>*NL*<~>reasoned<~>truth<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>latter<~>is<~>only<~>to<~>be<~>accepted<~>when<~>the<~>former<~>is<~>*NL*<~>too<~>remote<~>,<~>and<~>not<~>when<~>it<~>is<~>as<~>near<~>or<~>indeed<~>nearer<~>than<~>the<~>latter<~>.<~>*NL*<~>Accordingly<~>we<~>saw<~>above<~>that<~>,<~>as<~>a<~>matter<~>of<~>fact<~>,<~>in<~>the<~>case<~>of<~>logic<~>,<~>*NL*<~>in<~>which<~>the<~>immediate<~>knowledge<~>in<~>each<~>individual<~>case<~>lies<~>nearer<~>to<~>*NL*<~>hand<~>than<~>deduced<~>scientific<~>knowledge<~>,<~>we<~>always<~>conduct<~>our<~>thought<~>*NL*<~>according<~>to<~>our<~>immediate<~>knowledge<~>of<~>the<~>laws<~>of<~>thought<~>,<~>and<~>leave<~>*NL*<~>logic<~>unused<~>.<~>-LRB-<~>20<~>-RRB-<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>§<~>15<~>.<~>If<~>now<~>with<~>our<~>conviction<~>that<~>perception<~>is<~>the<~>primary<~>source<~>of<~>*NL*<~>all<~>evidence<~>,<~>and<~>that<~>only<~>direct<~>or<~>indirect<~>connection<~>with<~>it<~>is<~>*NL*<~>absolute<~>truth<~>;<~>and<~>further<~>,<~>that<~>the<~>shortest<~>way<~>to<~>this<~>is<~>always<~>the<~>*NL*<~>surest<~>,<~>as<~>every<~>interposition<~>of<~>concepts<~>means<~>exposure<~>to<~>many<~>*NL*<~>deceptions<~>;<~>if<~>,<~>I<~>say<~>,<~>we<~>now<~>turn<~>with<~>this<~>conviction<~>to<~>mathematics<~>,<~>as<~>*NL*<~>it<~>was<~>established<~>as<~>a<~>science<~>by<~>Euclid<~>,<~>and<~>has<~>remained<~>as<~>a<~>whole<~>to<~>*NL*<~>our<~>own<~>day<~>,<~>we<~>can<~>not<~>help<~>regarding<~>the<~>method<~>it<~>adopts<~>,<~>as<~>strange<~>and<~>*NL*<~>indeed<~>perverted<~>.<~>We<~>ask<~>that<~>every<~>logical<~>proof<~>shall<~>be<~>traced<~>back<~>to<~>*NL*<~>an<~>origin<~>in<~>perception<~>;<~>but<~>mathematics<~>,<~>on<~>the<~>contrary<~>,<~>is<~>at<~>great<~>*NL*<~>pains<~>deliberately<~>to<~>throw<~>away<~>the<~>evidence<~>of<~>perception<~>which<~>is<~>*NL*<~>peculiar<~>to<~>it<~>,<~>and<~>always<~>at<~>hand<~>,<~>that<~>it<~>may<~>substitute<~>for<~>it<~>a<~>*NL*<~>logical<~>demonstration<~>.<~>This<~>must<~>seem<~>to<~>us<~>like<~>the<~>action<~>of<~>a<~>man<~>who<~>*NL*<~>cuts<~>off<~>his<~>legs<~>in<~>order<~>to<~>go<~>on<~>crutches<~>,<~>or<~>like<~>that<~>of<~>the<~>prince<~>*NL*<~>in<~>the<~>``<~>Triumph<~>der<~>Empfindsamkeit<~>''<~>who<~>flees<~>from<~>the<~>beautiful<~>reality<~>*NL*<~>of<~>nature<~>,<~>to<~>delight<~>in<~>a<~>stage<~>scene<~>that<~>imitates<~>it<~>.<~>I<~>must<~>here<~>refer<~>*NL*<~>to<~>what<~>I<~>have<~>said<~>in<~>the<~>sixth<~>chapter<~>of<~>the<~>essay<~>on<~>the<~>principle<~>of<~>*NL*<~>sufficient<~>reason<~>,<~>and<~>take<~>for<~>granted<~>that<~>it<~>is<~>fresh<~>and<~>present<~>in<~>*NL*<~>the<~>memory<~>of<~>the<~>reader<~>;<~>so<~>that<~>I<~>may<~>link<~>my<~>observations<~>on<~>to<~>it<~>*NL*<~>without<~>explaining<~>again<~>the<~>difference<~>between<~>the<~>mere<~>ground<~>of<~>*NL*<~>knowledge<~>of<~>a<~>mathematical<~>truth<~>,<~>which<~>can<~>be<~>given<~>logically<~>,<~>and<~>the<~>*NL*<~>ground<~>of<~>being<~>,<~>which<~>is<~>the<~>immediate<~>connection<~>of<~>the<~>parts<~>of<~>space<~>*NL*<~>and<~>time<~>,<~>known<~>only<~>in<~>perception<~>.<~>It<~>is<~>only<~>insight<~>into<~>the<~>ground<~>of<~>*NL*<~>being<~>that<~>secures<~>satisfaction<~>and<~>thorough<~>knowledge<~>.<~>The<~>mere<~>ground<~>of<~>*NL*<~>knowledge<~>must<~>always<~>remain<~>superficial<~>;<~>it<~>can<~>afford<~>us<~>indeed<~>rational<~>*NL*<~>knowledge<~>that<~>a<~>thing<~>is<~>as<~>it<~>is<~>,<~>but<~>it<~>can<~>not<~>tell<~>why<~>it<~>is<~>so<~>.<~>*NL*<~>Euclid<~>chose<~>the<~>latter<~>way<~>to<~>the<~>obvious<~>detriment<~>of<~>the<~>science<~>.<~>F