<~>thus<~>makes<~>each<~>individual<~>*NL*<~>problem<~>an<~>axiom<~>.<~>Instead<~>of<~>the<~>demonstrations<~>that<~>fill<~>geometry<~>,<~>the<~>*NL*<~>whole<~>content<~>of<~>arithmetic<~>and<~>algebra<~>is<~>thus<~>simply<~>a<~>method<~>of<~>*NL*<~>abbreviating<~>counting<~>.<~>We<~>mentioned<~>above<~>that<~>our<~>immediate<~>perception<~>of<~>*NL*<~>numbers<~>in<~>time<~>extends<~>only<~>to<~>about<~>ten<~>.<~>Beyond<~>this<~>an<~>abstract<~>concept<~>*NL*<~>of<~>the<~>numbers<~>,<~>fixed<~>by<~>a<~>word<~>,<~>must<~>take<~>the<~>place<~>of<~>the<~>perception<~>;<~>*NL*<~>which<~>does<~>not<~>therefore<~>actually<~>occur<~>any<~>longer<~>,<~>but<~>is<~>only<~>indicated<~>*NL*<~>in<~>a<~>thoroughly<~>definite<~>manner<~>.<~>Yet<~>even<~>so<~>,<~>by<~>the<~>important<~>assistance<~>*NL*<~>of<~>the<~>system<~>of<~>figures<~>which<~>enables<~>us<~>to<~>represent<~>all<~>larger<~>numbers<~>*NL*<~>by<~>the<~>same<~>small<~>ones<~>,<~>intuitive<~>or<~>perceptive<~>evidence<~>of<~>every<~>sum<~>is<~>*NL*<~>made<~>possible<~>,<~>even<~>where<~>we<~>make<~>such<~>use<~>of<~>abstraction<~>that<~>not<~>only<~>*NL*<~>the<~>numbers<~>,<~>but<~>indefinite<~>quantities<~>and<~>whole<~>operations<~>are<~>thought<~>*NL*<~>only<~>in<~>the<~>abstract<~>and<~>indicated<~>as<~>so<~>thought<~>,<~>as<~>-LSB-<~>sqrt<~>-RSB-<~>-LRB-<~>r<~>^<~>b<~>-RRB-<~>so<~>that<~>*NL*<~>we<~>do<~>not<~>perform<~>them<~>,<~>but<~>merely<~>symbolise<~>them<~>.<~>*NL*<~>*NL*<~>We<~>might<~>establish<~>truth<~>in<~>geometry<~>also<~>,<~>through<~>pure<~>a<~>priori<~>*NL*<~>perception<~>,<~>with<~>the<~>same<~>right<~>and<~>certainty<~>as<~>in<~>arithmetic<~>.<~>It<~>is<~>in<~>*NL*<~>fact<~>always<~>this<~>necessity<~>,<~>known<~>through<~>perception<~>in<~>accordance<~>with<~>*NL*<~>the<~>principle<~>of<~>sufficient<~>reason<~>of<~>being<~>,<~>which<~>gives<~>to<~>geometry<~>its<~>*NL*<~>principal<~>evidence<~>,<~>and<~>upon<~>which<~>in<~>the<~>consciousness<~>of<~>every<~>one<~>,<~>the<~>*NL*<~>certainty